@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Client (User)" as Client
actor "Admin (User)" as Admin

package "RealAssist Frontend" {
  rectangle "Frontend App" as Frontend
}

package "External Systems" {
  rectangle "Backend API (FastAPI)" as Backend
  rectangle "Database (MongoDB)" as DB
  rectangle "Payment Gateway (Stripe)" as Payment
  rectangle "AI/ML Services (RAG / Classifier)" as AI
}

Client --> Frontend : Browse UI / Login / Make Payment / Chat
Admin --> Frontend : Admin Dashboard / Manage Leads
Frontend --> Backend : REST calls (auth, leads, payments, assistant)
Backend --> DB : read/write (users, leads, payments, updates)
Backend --> AI : request classification / RAG retrieval
Backend --> Payment : initiate & verify payments
Payment --> Backend : webhooks / verification

note right of Frontend
Mapping to code:
- UI: src/pages/*, src/components/*
- Mock API layer: src/services/api.ts
- Auth: src/hooks/useAuth.ts
- Chatbot UI: src/components/ui/Chatbot.tsx
end note

@enduml
